If testRun == false, regular clock rates apply (1000UL).
Pause Protocol: If a pause is requested during active cooking states, freeze the countdown clock and any active processing iterations. Keep track of elapsed time offsets while paused (pauseStartTime) and cleanly add those offsets to stateStartTime and oneSecondClock upon resuming to eliminate temporal drift.
