Degas State Initiation: Send a 2-second longPress to srvRunReset, 7 shortPress loops to srvMenu, 10 shortPress loops to srvMinus, and 1 shortPress to srvRunReset. Halt script operations for 10 seconds via delay(10000) to complete internal host alignments, and close by firing another 2-second longPress to srvRunReset. Sub-divide cycles into blocks of up to 30 minutes.
Proof State Initiation: Send a 2-second longPress to srvRunReset strictly at the absolute chronological beginning of the phase (skip on consecutive continuous loop sub-shifts). Sub-divide cycles into chunks capped at 60 minutes.
Bake State Initiation: Send a 2-second longPress to srvRunReset, 13 shortPress loops to srvMenu, 10 shortPress loops to srvMinus, and 1 shortPress to srvRunReset. Sub-divide execution tracking into chunks capped at 60 minutes.
Pulse Dynamics: Define a shortPress as a LOW pulse for 200ms followed by a HIGH float for 300ms. Define a longPress as a LOW pulse for 200ms, a HIGH float for 300ms, an active LOW anchor for 2000ms, and a final recovery HIGH float for 1000ms.
